column7: 3a = mild to moderate paraparesis or hemiparesis
column8: 3b = severe monoparesis: BMRC grade 2 or less
column9: 4a = marked paraparesis or hemiparesis: usually BMRC grade 2
column11: 4c = monoplegia: BMRC grade 0 or 1 in one limb
column14: 5c = marked tetraparesis: BMRC grade 2 or less

column10: 4 = severe truncal ataxia and in 3 or 4 limbs
